  "texts": [
    "c) Combating Missing Modalities: Multimodal systems face challenges with missing modalities, negatively impacting performance.",
    "Researchers proposed methods for missing modality imputation and performance improvement.",
    "[78] uses cascaded residual autoencoder (CRA) for missing modality imputation, stacking residual autoencoders (RAs) that iteratively output the difference between incomplete and complete data.",
    "[79] learns robust joint representations by translating between modalities, using a translation network to establish a consistent, robust common space.",
    "This approach allows the system to handle missing modalities at test time by inferring them from available modalities.d) Networking and system support for AI inference: The scope of support for AI spans the entire lifecycle of AI services, from data collection and model training to model inference [80]."
